Yes, there is a MiniGL project. I am currently working on it. The work is
for our Heretic II and Shogo ports. We will, however, release the MiniGL
library to the public later. I'm about halfway through no.

It will basically be a graphics library disguising itself as a GL
implementation. It will have MANY drawbacks from the full thing, just the
basics like transformation, texture mapping, a bit of buffer management
